httpServletRequestX.accept.contentType
Class AcceptContenType

java.lang.Object
  httpServletRequestX.accept.contentType.AcceptContenType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<AcceptContenType>
public class AcceptContenType
extends Object
implements Comparable<AcceptContenType>

Accept header content type implementation to the HTTP 1.1 specification. Sorting the priority of all content-types is based on the quality flag. An missing quality flag will be automatically set to the highest priority. TODO: level flag is currently ignored. http://www.http.specification.de/

Author:
Marco Reinwarth
